+{"id":"bd-5if6f","title":"string: bound tokenizer delimiter scans","description":"strtok, strtok_r, and strsep scan delimiter strings with known_remaining(delim) only when repair mode is active. A tracked malloc-backed delimiter without a NUL can therefore be scanned past its allocation in strict paths before constructing delimiter slices. Mirror the wcstok delimiter-bound fix: always use known_remaining(delim) when available, reject tracked unterminated delimiters before building the delimiter slice, and add regression tests.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"codex-string-delim-bounds","created_at":"2026-04-29T04:04:16.296711618Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-29T04:12:31.757591614Z","closed_at":"2026-04-29T04:12:31.755011961Z","close_reason":"Bounded strtok/strtok_r/strsep delimiter scans with tracked unterminated delimiter regressions. Validation: rustfmt --check; git diff --check; rch cargo test -p frankenlibc-abi --test string_abi_test tracked_unterminated_delimiter; rch cargo test -p frankenlibc-abi --test conformance_diff_string_mut diff_strtok_r_cases; rch cargo check -p frankenlibc-abi --all-targets; rch cargo clippy -p frankenlibc-abi --all-targets -- -D warnings; ubs touched files (0 critical).","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["parity","safety","string"]}
 {"id":"bd-5jsr","title":"resolv: gai_suspend degenerate request sets should ignore timeout validation and preserve errno","description":"Host glibc returns EAI_ALLDONE with errno unchanged for gai_suspend on already-complete degenerate request sets even when the timeout is invalid (for example tv_nsec=1_000_000_000 or tv_sec<0). FrankenLibC currently matches that behavior, but the ABI regression suite only covers NULL timeout cases. Add focused tests and document the timeout-ignored semantics in unistd_abi.rs.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-21T06:50:23.785286766Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-21T06:53:14.283181440Z","closed_at":"2026-04-21T06:53:14.280876516Z","close_reason":"Locked down host-parity gai_suspend timeout semantics for already-complete degenerate request sets, verifying that invalid timespec values are ignored and errno stays unchanged; verified locally and via rch.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
